# Lesson 05 Livebook: The Pre-Origin Model

This notebook keeps the full event-sourcing stack and adds a pre-origin completion step.

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:pre_origin_model, path: "../05_pre_origin_model"}
])
```

## Load The Final Trace

```elixir
events = PreOriginModel.sample_trace()
```

## Inspect The Gap And Dependency Layers

```elixir
%{
  gaps: PreOriginModel.GapScanner.project(events),
  inferred: PreOriginModel.InferenceProjector.project(events),
  dependencies: PreOriginModel.DependencyAnalyzer.project(events)
}
```

## Complete The Trace

```elixir
completed_events = PreOriginModel.HorizonCompleter.complete(events)
```

## Reinterpret The Beginning

```elixir
%{
  timeline: PreOriginModel.CosmicTimeline.project(completed_events),
  replay: PreOriginModel.Replayer.replay(completed_events),
  anomalies: PreOriginModel.AnomalyDetector.project(completed_events),
  pre_origin: PreOriginModel.PreOriginProjection.project(completed_events)
}
```
